assetProfile.longBusinessSummary: Takeda iP Holdings Co.,Ltd. provides printing services in Japan. It designs, plans, and publishes catalogs and pamphlets, art prints, and books. It is also involved in the multi-media planning business; design, manufacture, and sale of semiconductor-related masks and machinery and equipment; and sale of stationery, daily goods, etc. The company was formerly known as Takeda Printing Co., Ltd. and changed its name to Takeda iP Holdings Co.,Ltd. in April 2023. Takeda iP Holdings Co.,Ltd. was founded in 1924 and is headquartered in Nagoya, Japan.
